cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image transformation using deep convolutional features, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of pre-trained convnets and linear interpolation also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves manipulating and modifying images, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of deep learning techniques for image transformation could also be relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
